Detailed Description

cvmx_pko_mem_count0

Notes: Total number of packets seen by PKO, per port A write to this address will clear the entry whose index is specified as COUNT[5:0]. This CSR is a memory of 44 entries, and thus, the PKO_REG_READ_IDX CSR must be written before any CSR read operations to this address can be performed. A read of any entry that has not been previously written is illegal and will result in unpredictable CSR read data.
